title: Mike Wilson: An Unsatisfying Market for Bulls and Bears?
description: On today’s episode, Chief Investment Officer Mike Wilson says both bulls and bears were likely a bit frustrated trying to trade last week's sell-off and rally. So what’s the next move for investors?
